OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778230885
OL,3,CCoroner awaits evidence as
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Liam Payne's death
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FSenior coroner Crispin Butler told the
OL,8,Fhearing on Thursday there had been no
OL,9,Fupdates since the last pre-inquest
OL,10,Freview in January last year, when he
OL,11,Fsaid he would seek full reports and
OL,12,Feyewitness statements before a final
OL,13,Finquest.
OL,15,F"Since the last pre-inquest review, we
OL,16,Fhave had no further disclosure of
OL,17,Fevidence from Argentina via the
OL,18,FForeign, Commonwealth & Development
OL,19,FOffice," Mr Butler said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@HO]
