PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778230885
OL,3,CCoroner awaits evidence as
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Liam Payne's death
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,F"My understanding is the
OL,8,Finvestigations are continuing and I
OL,9,Fawait further developments.
OL,11,F"Documentation received prior to this
OL,12,Fpre-inquest hearing have undergone a
OL,13,Fprocess of translation," he added.
OL,15,FHe also said he would share the
OL,16,Frelevant documents with Liam Payne's
OL,17,Ffamily, who did not attend the brief
OL,18,Fhearing at Beaconsfield Coroner's
OL,19,FCourt on Thursday.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@XO]
