OL,3,CCoroner awaits evidence as
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Liam Payne's death
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FA post mortem report said that Payne
OL,8,Fdied of multiple traumas and "internal
OL,9,Fand external haemorrhage" after
OL,10,Ffalling from a third floor balcony of
OL,11,Fthe Casa Sur Hotel in Buenos Aires.
OL,13,FIn February 2025, a court in Argentina
OL,14,Fdropped charges of criminal negligence
OL,15,Fagainst three of the five people who
OL,16,Fhad been charged in connection with
OL,17,Fhis death.
OL,19,FThe inquest was adjourned until a
OL,20,Ffurther pre-inquest review at the
OL,21,Fstart of December.
